  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270200</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>できたわ……
私が求めていた、
究極の光……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've done it... This is what I've been
yearning for... The ultimate light...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おめでとうございます！
測定値は想定の1.18倍です！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Congratulations! The output is about 1.18
times stronger than what we expected.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この偉大な発明は
博士の名前を歴史上に
刻むことでしょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With an accomplishment this huge,
I'm sure Doctor Meltia's name will
make it into the annals of history!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>名誉、というものかしら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I am so very honored, I suppose.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、そんなもの
特別欲しいと
思ったわけじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...this isn't the special thing I yearned for.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……私が欲しかったのは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...What I truly crave...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……誰かの喜ぶ顔……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Is simply...anothers delight
at what I do, for a change...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Did you say something?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, it's nothing...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お父様は
喜んでくれるかしら？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you think father will be pleased at this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？
ああ、バンディ将軍ですか？
そうですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Oh, general Bandi? Yeah I think so.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>将軍どころか、
パレスグドラの全国民が
喜んでくれていますよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not just the general, but all of Palace
Gudora is overjoyed because of this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何しろ、この力があれば、
戦争は終わるんですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I mean, with power like this,
we can finally end the war!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうね……これでお父様の望む
デリス・カーラーンの平和が
得られるんですもの……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right...With this, father will be
able to accomplish his one wish for
a peaceful Derris Kharlan...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
